data.description: Welcome to 12040 Tralee Road #301 in the desirable community of Tralee Forest offering a secure elevator building and superb location! The open concept living area features a cozy fireplace that seamlessly connects to the dining room, making it perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings at home. Eat-in kitchen boasts ample cabinetry and a breakfast room with access to the private balcony. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself. It features an en-suite full bath, and a spacious walk-in closet offering ample storage space. Second bedroom is well-appointed with a walk in closet and offers a comfortable space for guests or family members. A full bath and a spacious laundry room conclude this wonderful home. Community Amenities: Enjoy being in close proximity to a vast variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment options at nearby Hunt Valley, Towson Town Center, Mays Chapel Roundwood Shopping Center, and Graul’s Market. A short drive to Baltimore's Inner Harbor, Camden Yards, and M&T Stadium. Major commuter routes include I-695, I-95, and I-83.
